author: Jonathan Sawyer
title: Nike’s Air Woven Drops in Three New SS17 Colorways
text:
Visit the original post to see all 3 images from this gallery. 
Brand: Nike
Model: Air Woven
Key Features: Slip-on design, woven nylon upper, leather and suede pull tabs, Air-cushioned midsole
Release Date: Available now
Price: $160 USD
Availability: Available now at select NSW retailers including Undefeated .
Editor’s Notes: Nike Sportswear returns with a trio of in-house Air Woven releases for the warm weather season. The low-top slip-on arrives in a standout multicolor look, as well as binary blue and black/white/grey iterations.
Look for these to be a popular play during the spring and summer months.
